Bus Schedule Information http://victorycasinocruises.com/transportation/busses 

Make your reservations online, print your boarding pass and bypass the lines at ticketing to get right on the ship! www.webtogate.com 


For pricing information click here http://victorycasinocruises.com/about-us/cruise-schedule

More than 600 slots and 30 table games featuring Craps and Roulette as well as Blackjack-EZ Bacarrat-3 card poker, Texas Hold'em and MORE! Florida's only Sports Book! Three lounges featuring CLUB V on the fourth deck. Buffet and ala cart dining with LIVE ENTERTAINMENT! Main attraction...Florida's BEST PLayers Club! For the comfort of our guests, we offer non-smoking on decks 1 and 4.
